        <mxCell id="aws_services_a" value="AWS Services account A:&#xa;• Secrets Manager (ESO source)&#xa;• ECR shopxpress-pro/{gateway,products,orders}&#xa;• S3 backend TF state + S3 Velero source bucket&#xa;• KMS CMK envelope EKS secret + S3 + Velero&#xa;• CloudTrail organization trail (delegated admin)&#xa;• Security Hub delegated administrator&#xa;• GuardDuty + Config + Falco DaemonSet&#xa;• IAM Identity Center (Phase 1+) — RBAC + ABAC" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF2CC;strokeColor=#D6B656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
